NOTICE:

This is the open-source edition (v2.0) of AirBridge.

Originally developed as NextAir v1.0 (2016-2019) by Werapol Bejranonda and
Pathawee Somsak. Reorganized for open-source release in 2025 by Werapol
Bejranonda.

The commercial version (v1.0) with patented smart energy-saving features
remains proprietary and is available at: https://wenext.net/

Features exclusive to the commercial version include:
- Patented smart cutting algorithms
- Baseline learning and adaptation
- Remote monitoring (MQTT)
- Email reporting
- 20-50% energy savings
- Professional support

This open-source version provides basic IR relay functionality only.

